"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-09-Chinese-paper-cutting-artistry-shines-at-Paris-Olympics-1vV8gsHa0P6-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  As the Paris Olympics is abuzz with excitement, Shen Yanli, a talented paper-cutting artist from Huzhou in east China, infuses her unique flair into this global celebration of sportsmanship and athleticism.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huzhou\"}, {\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_China\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"east China\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her exquisite paper-cuttings showcase traditional designs like the \\\"Mulberry Fish Dragon\\\" and the 2024 Olympic mascot, Phryge, seamlessly blending Chinese and French elements.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9544906962652135, \"rank\": 0.04272987615185649, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9931026679